# E2E report discipline (read-before · write-after)

**Law:** `brain-os/law/enforcement/SOURCEA_E2E_WEEKLY_CHECKLIST_LOCKED_v1.md`  
**Registry:** `data/sourcea-e2e-check-registry-v1.json`  
**Runner:** `scripts/sourcea_e2e_run_v1.py`  
**Last report:** `~/.sina/sourcea-e2e-last-report-v1.json`

## Before any E2E

```bash
python3 scripts/sourcea_e2e_run_v1.py --read-last --json
```

Read `blockers[]`, `stale_checks`, `summary` — do not re-run fresh PASS unless founder says `--force`.

## Run one bundle (not validator chains)

```bash
python3 scripts/sourcea_e2e_run_v1.py --bundle <id> --write-report --json
python3 scripts/sourcea_e2e_run_v1.py --cadence weekly --write-report --json
```

## After E2E

Report must land in `~/.sina/sourcea-e2e-last-report-v1.json` + `~/.sina/e2e-logs/` — **not `/tmp` only**.

## Mac founder session (INCIDENT-039)

- **Allowed:** T0_probe · T1_fast (`mac_daily_smoke` bundle)
- **Forbidden:** T2+ without ship window — route to cloud CI

## Forbidden

- Chained `validate-* && validate-*` to prove chat answers
- Full E2E in Brain chat (`BRAIN_NO_FULL_E2E_SHELL_LOCKED_v1.md`)
- Re-run when last report shows fresh PASS
